data.value: Welcome to the iOS Tools Section! As noted in the release notes, this section is a fill-in for cydia. If you have a jailbroken iOS device and don't want to use our cydia repo, you can use The Elite Patch to install the same patch. We are working hard to allow this to work on Jailbroken and non-jailbroken devices, but keep in mind with Apple's strict security policy for apps, this will take some time. So enjoy The Elite Patch for iOS!
